1 actions with respect to certain per– and polyfluoroalkyl substances; and generally
2 relating to per– and polyfluoroalkyl substances and sewage sludge.
3 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
4 Article – Environment
5 Section 9–201(a), (l), and (m) and 9–230
